public interface LongCompution
extends NumberCompution
Long value Compution, includes Getter, Observer.

NOT includes Setter.

    • NumberObservable.multiply(NumberObservable)

  • To comparative-compute,

    • NumberObservable.computeIsNotEqualTo(NumberObservable)
